    <item>
      <title>马克龙部长对法国左翼的最低工资计划表示欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/macron-minister-warms-to-the-french-left-s-minimum-wage-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国内政部长杰拉德·达尔马南表示，最低工资标准可能会提高，这为争夺下届政府政策影响力的左翼阵营的一项关键提议打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/macron-minister-warms-to-the-french-left-s-minimum-wage-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列内塔尼亚胡将于周二会见正在康复的拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/israel-s-netanyahu-will-meet-with-recovering-biden-on-tuesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本杰明内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示，他将于周二在华盛顿会见美国总统乔拜登，此前一天，以色列总理将向国会联席会议发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/israel-s-netanyahu-will-meet-with-recovering-biden-on-tuesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰军队面临包围风险 放弃顿涅茨克村庄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-ukraine-kyiv-s-forces-flee-donetsk-village-to-avoid-encirclement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DeepState 地图服务在 Telegram 上表示，乌克兰军队撤出了顿涅茨克地区的普罗赫雷斯村，因为他们面临被俄罗斯军队围困的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-ukraine-kyiv-s-forces-flee-donetsk-village-to-avoid-encirclement</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
